<SYNC Start=20630><P Class=ENUSCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=21375><P Class=ENUSCC>-Wanna fuck?<br>-Yes. You do, too. Come look at this.
<SYNC Start=24995><P Class=ENUSCC>&nbsp;
