<SYNC Start=42293><P Class=ENUSCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=44166><P Class=ENUSCC>The CIA, FBI,
<SYNC Start=46206><P Class=ENUSCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=46291><P Class=ENUSCC>and Interpol also have agents<br>that look friendly.
<SYNC Start=49041><P Class=ENUSCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=49125><P Class=ENUSCC>Come on, man. They're tourists.<br>You can see it in their faces.
<SYNC Start=52075><P Class=ENUSCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=55458><P Class=ENUSCC>My love.
<SYNC Start=56288><P Class=ENUSCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=57791><P Class=ENUSCC>We need to socialize.
<SYNC Start=59331><P Class=ENUSCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=60208><P Class=ENUSCC>I'm serious. Couples need a social life.
<SYNC Start=62578><P Class=ENUSCC>&nbsp;
