<SYNC Start=94998><P Class=ENUSCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=96791><P Class=ENUSCC>Hey!
<SYNC Start=98581><P Class=ENUSCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=98666><P Class=ENUSCC>Hello, my friends!
<SYNC Start=100706><P Class=ENUSCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=110416><P Class=ENUSCC>Rio! Rio! Rio!
