<SYNC Start=1318625><P Class=ENUSCC>And I didn't open my eyes<br>until this morning.
<SYNC Start=1320375><P Class=ENUSCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1320958><P Class=ENUSCC>Alicia woke me up.
<SYNC Start=1322378><P Class=ENUSCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1324000><P Class=ENUSCC>Well, what?
<SYNC Start=1324880><P Class=ENUSCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1327041><P Class=ENUSCC>Where is my red jumper?
<SYNC Start=1328541><P Class=ENUSCC>&nbsp;
