<SYNC Start=1332960><P Class=ENUSCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1333041><P Class=ENUSCC>So if we suspect anything, the key words<br>will be "quick vacation".
<SYNC Start=1336791><P Class=ENUSCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1337666><P Class=ENUSCC><i>Rest a little bit more.</i>
<SYNC Start=1338956><P Class=ENUSCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1339541><P Class=ENUSCC>Take a hot bath.
<SYNC Start=1341001><P Class=ENUSCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1343000><P Class=ENUSCC>You deserve a quick vacation.
<SYNC Start=1344670><P Class=ENUSCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1351250><P Class=ENUSCC>A GPS beacon in a tooth implant.
